BobUI 3.3.6 is a bug-fix release. It maintains both forward and backward
compatibility (source and binary) with BobUI 3.3.5, 3.3.4, BobUI 3.3.3, BobUI 3.3.2,
BobUI 3.3.1 and BobUI 3.3.0.

****************************************************************************
*                           General                                        *
****************************************************************************

Platforms
---------

- It is now possible to build BobUI 3.3.6 on Intel Macs. A universal
  BobUI build however requires manual work by 'lipo'-ing a PPC BobUI
  and an Intel BobUI together.

Compilers
---------

- The build key when building BobUI with gcc 4.x has changed. This means
  you will have to either recompile your plugins or change the configure
  script to not reduce the gcc version string to '4'.


Translations
------------

Various BobUI translations contributed by Novell.
